This bootstrap repository contains architecture documentation and Kotlin
skeleton code for a GNSS receiver recorder, NTRIP client, correction router,
receiver controller and base-calibration workflow companion.

Third-party dependencies must be documented in docs/third-party-licenses.md
before release builds are distributed.

RTKLIB-EX real-time integration is planned. This repository currently contains
RTKLIB routing/API foundation code only; no RTKLIB-EX upstream source snapshot
or native binary is bundled yet. A development helper can create a local pinned
RTKLIB-EX checkout, but that checkout is not part of the distributed source
tree unless explicitly added and documented in a later release.
